      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The Chakra Threads animating the target light up and become more clearly visible, granting anyone trying to see than a +8 bonus to the Spot check to do so. The creature who created the Threads can make a save to reduce the bonus to +2.</p>\n\n\n\n",
